  "prompt": "What is the best type of exercise for weight loss?",
  "response": "The most effective exercise for weight loss typically combines cardiovascular activities and strength training. Some of the best exercises include:\n\n1. High-Intensity Interval Training (HIIT)\n- Burns calories quickly\n- Boosts metabolism\n- Can be done with various exercises\n\n2. Running/Jogging\n- High calorie burn\n- Improves cardiovascular health\n- Accessible and requires minimal equipment\n\n3. Swimming\n- Full-body workout\n- Low impact on joints\n- High calorie expenditure\n\n4. Strength Training\n- Builds muscle mass\n- Increases metabolism\n- Burns calories even after exercise\n\n5. Cycling\n- Low impact\n- Good for cardiovascular health\n- Can be done indoors or outdoors\n\n6. Brisk Walking\n- Low intensity but effective\n- Suitable for all fitness levels\n- Easy to maintain\n\nThe most important factors are:\n- Consistency\n- Enjoyment of the exercise\n- Combining cardio and strength training\n- Maintaining a calorie deficit through diet\n\nAlways consult a healthcare professional before starting a new exercise program, especially if you have pre-existing health conditions.",
